text: Chao Jou (born 23 March 1995) is a Taiwanese karateka. In 2014, she won one of the bronze medals in the women's kumite 68 kg event at the 2014 Asian Games held in Incheon, South Korea. In 2018, she lost her bronze medal match against Kayo Someya of Japan in that event at the 2018 Asian Games held in Jakarta, Indonesia.
